_struct.pdbx_model_details
;This model was generated unsupervised by the SWISS-MODEL homology-modelling pipeline for the SWISS-MODEL Repository, a database of annotated 3D protein structure models. The modelled homo-pentamer covers following UniProtKB entries:

  - D0LHE5/ BMCP_HALO1, Bacterial microcompartment shell vertex protein

Estimated model accuracy of this model is 0.775, calculated by SWISS-MODEL as Global Model Quality Estimate (GMQE).
;
_struct.pdbx_structure_determination_methodology computational
_struct.title 'Model for UniProtKB entries D0LHE5'
